name: Draconic Dissent (Battle for Baldur's Gate Commander Precon Decklist)

main.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate
main.name: Firkraag, Cunning Instigator
main.oracle_text:
Flying, haste
Whenever one or more Dragons you control attack an opponent, goad target creature that player controls.
Whenever a creature deals combat damage to one of your opponents, if that creature had to attack this combat, you put a +1/+1 counter on Firkraag, Cunning Instigator and you draw a card.

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate
card.name: Command Tower
card.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
card.flavor_text: Durlag's Tower is filled with enough treasure to last a lifetime, and enough traps to drastically shorten that lifetime.

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate
card.name: Arcane Signet
card.oracle_text: {T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander's color identity.
card.flavor_text:
"To feel no constraint but the four points of a compass, to tread a path that only you can find . . . these are the flavors of power I've learned to savor."
—Keon, horizon walker

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate
card.name: Wayfarer's Bauble
card.oracle_text: {2}, {T}, Sacrifice Wayfarer's Bauble: Search your library for a basic land card, put that card onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
card.flavor_text: Druids hold certain plants to be sacred and use their leaves and wood as a spellcasting focus.

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate
card.name: Burnished Hart
card.oracle_text: {3}, Sacrifice Burnished Hart: Search your library for up to two basic land cards, put them onto the battlefield tapped, then shuffle.
card.flavor_text: Not born of nature, but deeply connected to it nonetheless.

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate
card.name: Mind Stone
card.oracle_text:
{T}: Add {C}.
{1}, {T}, Sacrifice Mind Stone: Draw a card.
card.flavor_text:
"I don't study it because I want answers; I study it because there is beauty in pursuing the unknown."
—Misvaad, Candlekeep librarian

card.oracle_text:
Enchant creature
Enchanted creature gets +2/+2 and is goaded. (It attacks each combat if able and attacks a player other than you if able.)
Whenever enchanted creature attacks, you scry 2.

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate

card.oracle_text:
Enchant creature

card.name: Astral Dragon
card.oracle_text:
Flying

card.oracle_text:
(Gain the next level as a sorcery to add its ability.)

card.name: Loot Dispute

When Loot Dispute enters, you take the initiative and create a Treasure token.

Flash

card.oracle_text: Target player draws three cards. Then that player discards two cards unless they discard a land card.
card.flavor_text: "Four parts molten bronze, yes . . . one part frozen mercury, yes, yes . . . but then what?"

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate
card.name: Chain Reaction

card.flavor_text:
"We train for the improbable, like lightning striking the same place twice, or striking everywhere at once."
—Nundari, Sea Gate militia captain

card.oracle_text:

Flying, haste

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate
card.name: Drakuseth, Maw of Flames
card.oracle_text:
Flying

card.flavor_text:
"Spread out, you idiots! Spread out!"
—Marsden, party leader, last words

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate
card.name: Keiga, the Tide Star
card.oracle_text:
Flying

card.name: Ryusei, the Falling Star

Flying

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate
card.name: Sprite Dragon
card.oracle_text:
Flying, haste

card.flavor_text: Size of a pixie, rage of a hellkite.

card.name: Thunder Dragon

Flying

At the beginning of combat on your turn, choose an opponent at random that Territorial Hellkite didn't attack during your last combat. Territorial Hellkite attacks that player this combat if able. If you can't choose an opponent this way, tap Territorial Hellkite.

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate

Flying

card.name: Warmonger Hellkite
card.oracle_text:
Flying
All creatures attack each combat if able.
{1}{R}: Attacking creatures get +1/+0 until end of turn.
card.flavor_text: Its wings beat to the howls of war and fan the fires of rage.

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate

card.oracle_text:

card.flavor_text:
"Holy places are no longer sanctuary from death, and death is no longer sanctuary from anything."
—Thalia, Knight-Cathar

card.set_name: Commander Legends: Battle for Baldur's Gate

Forge — Put two +1/+1 counters on target creature. (Leads to: Trap!, Arena)
Lost Well — Scry 2. (Leads to: Arena, Stash)
Trap! — Target player loses 5 life. (Leads to: Archives)
Arena — Goad target creature. (Leads to: Archives, Catacombs)
Stash — Create a Treasure token. (Leads to: Catacombs)
Archives — Draw a card. (Leads to: Throne of the Dead Three)
Catacombs — Create a 4/1 black Skeleton creature token with menace. (Leads to: Throne of the Dead Three)
Throne of the Dead Three — Reveal the top ten cards of your library. Put a creature card from among them onto the battlefield with three +1/+1 counters on it. It gains hexproof until your next turn. Then shuffle.

card_faces.name: The Initiative
card_faces.oracle_text:
Whenever one or more creatures a player controls deal combat damage to you, that player takes the initiative.
Whenever you take the initiative and at the beginning of your upkeep, venture into Undercity. (If you're in a dungeon, advance to the next room. If you're not, enter Undercity. You can take the initiative even if you already have it.)
